    "html": "<!DOCTYPE html><html style=\"font-size: 85px;\"><head>\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1\">\n    <meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\">\n    <meta name=\"renderer\" content=\"webkit\">\n    <title>清华大学建筑学院</title>\n    <meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"清华大学建筑学院,建筑学院,世界一流,建筑学,中国特色，城市规划，建筑系\">\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"清华大学是中国著名高等学府，是中国高层次人才培养和科学技术研究的重要基地。清华大学的前身是清华学堂，成立于1911年。截至2017年，清华大学设有20个学院、58个系，已成为一所具有理学、工学、文学、艺术学、历史学、哲学、经济学、管理学、法学、教育学和医学等学科门类的综合性、研究型、开放式大学。截至2017年8月31号，清华大学在学学生总数为47762人，其中本科生15619人、硕士生19062人、博士生13081人。\">\n   \n    <link href=\"/sites/css/font.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n    <link href=\"/sites/css/index.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n    <link href=\"/sites/css/phone.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/sites/js/swiper/swiper-3.4.2.min.css\">\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/sites/js/jquery-3.3.1.min.js\"></script>\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/sites/js/js.js\"></script>\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/sites/js/swiper/swiper-3.4.2.jquery.min.js\"></script>\n</head>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<body>\n<div class=\"headD\"></div>\n   \n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"head\">\n    <div class=\"wal\">\n        <a href=\"\" class=\"logo\"></a>\n        <a href=\"javascript:;\" class=\"navA\"></a>\n        <dl class=\"btn\">\n            <dd><a href=\"/column/INDEX\" class=\"on\">CN</a></dd>\n            <dd><a href=\"/column/Home\">EN</a></dd>\n            \n            \n \n            \n            \n            <dd class=\"search\" value=\"搜索\"> \n              <form name=\"form1\" id=\"search-form-header\" action=\"/column/search\" target=\"_blank\" method=\"post\">\n                   <div class=\"input\">    <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"curpage\" value=\"1\">\n\t               <input name=\"key\" type=\"text\" class=\"inp\" value=\"\" onfocus=\"this.value=''\" onblur=\"if(this.value==''){this.value='';}\">\n                </div>  \n\t         </form>\n        \n           </dd>  \n            <div class=\"submit\">      \n                 <a id=\"searchbtn\" href=\"javascript:;\" onclick=\"$('#search-form-header').submit();\" class=\"btn\" title=\"搜索\">搜索</a>\n           </div> \n      \n            \n        </dl>\n        <div class=\"nav\">\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/INDEX\">首页</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/jj\">简介</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/dt\">动态</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/xs\">系所</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/zs\">招生</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/jx\">教学</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/ky\">科研</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/rw\">人物</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/jl\">交流</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/lj\">链接</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"characterShow_01\">\n    <div class=\"wal\">\n         <div class=\"info\"><a href=\"/column/INDEX\">首页</a><a href=\"/column/rw\"><b>·</b>人物</a>  <a href=\"/column/sz\"><b>·</b>师资</a>  <a href=\"/column/rw_csgh\"><b>·</b>城市规划系</a>  </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"name\">邵磊</div>\n        <div class=\"msg\">\n            电话：86-10-62796993 <br>\n            传真：86-10-68771897 <br>\n            E-mail：IHCS2009@gmail.com\n        </div>\n    \n       <div class=\"img\"><img src=\"/upload_files/image/1572140595848_47.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\n   \n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"wal characterShow\">\n   \n     <div class=\"content\"><p style=\"line-height: 24px;page-break-after: avoid;margin-left: 28px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"></span></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;page-break-after: avoid;margin: 2px 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-weight: 700\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">研究和教学方向</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">城市规划与设计</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">居住问题研究</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;page-break-after: avoid;margin: 2px 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-weight: 700\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">教育简历</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"> 1991.09-2003.07&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">清华大学建筑学院学习，获得建筑学学士与工学博士学位</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;page-break-after: avoid;margin: 2px 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-weight: 700\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">专业履历</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;page-break-after: avoid;margin-left: 28px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">清华大学建筑学院</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><br></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;page-break-after: avoid;margin-left: 28px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><br></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;page-break-after: avoid;margin-left: 28px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">研究项目</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">1.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">河北省农村新民居规划建设研究（<span>2009</span>年<span>4-5</span>月）</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">国家“十一五”科技支撑项目：农村住宅规划设计与建设标准研究负责子课题：村镇住宅建筑设计模块化技术与软件开发（<span>2008-2011</span>年）</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">3.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">招商地产中国住房与城市发展研究</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">4.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">中国<span>-</span>新加坡政府合作项目天津生态城总体规划生态社区专项（<span>2007-2008</span>年）</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">5.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">《</span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">保障性住房工业化设计建造关键技术研究与示范》，“十二五”国家科技支撑计划课题</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">6.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">《北京市公租房需求调研》，北京市住房保障办公室，</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: red\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">7.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: red\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">《建立中关村人才公租房建设标准》，北京市住房保障办公室</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: red\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">8.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: red\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">《机构老年人生活居住环境设计模式研究》，中国社会福利协会，</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: red\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">9.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: red\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">《陕西华阴适老化社区发展研究》，</span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">中海（渭南）投资有限责任公司</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: red\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"> 10.</span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">Making the Clean Energy &nbsp;City(</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: red\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">建设清洁能源城市<span>)</span>，清华大学、<span>MIT</span>联合研究项目，</span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">美国能源基金会</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: red\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">11.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: red\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">Low Carbon Urban Design(</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: red\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">低碳城市设计研究<span>)</span>，清华大学<span>-MIT-</span>剑桥大学三校低碳联盟课题</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;page-break-after: avoid;margin-left: 28px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">课程教学</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 26px;line-height: 24px;margin: 2px 0\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">本科教学</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 27px;line-height: 24px;margin: 2px 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">住区规划与住宅设计<span>(</span>本科生秋季课程，<span>90</span>人，<span>4</span>学分</span><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">)</span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 27px;line-height: 24px;margin: 2px 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">房地产概论（本科生春季课程，<span>90</span>人，<span>1</span>学分）</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 26px;line-height: 24px;margin: 2px 0\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">研究生教学</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 27px;line-height: 24px;margin: 2px 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">近现代住宅<span>&nbsp;(</span>秋季课程，学生<span>40</span>人</span><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">)</span></span></span></p><h3 style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 28px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">国际交流</span></span></h3><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"> 1.2006年9月－2007年9月，美国哈佛大学设计研究生院访问学者</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"> 2.2007年2月－2007年6月，美国麻省理工学院建筑学院研究生二年级建筑设计Studio指导教师&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">3.2005年7月，东京大学城市可持续发展研究中心（CSUR）设计课程指导教师</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"> 4.2005年3月，第二届中亚历史城市规划与保护学术会议中、日、韩三国学生联合Studio指导教师</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"> 5.2004年9月，应日本东京大学邀请，参加“亚洲城市的可持续发展”学术会议，做“北京旧城保护政策研究”的学术报告</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"> 6.2012年9月5日&nbsp;The&nbsp;Sixth&nbsp;Session&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;World&nbsp;Urban&nbsp;Forum,&nbsp;Naples,Italy, &nbsp;《Urban&nbsp;Housing&nbsp;Reform&nbsp;and&nbsp;Security&nbsp;Housing&nbsp;System&nbsp;in&nbsp;China》</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"> 7.2012年12月2日 </span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: red\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"> International&nbsp;Workshop&nbsp;\"Agenda&nbsp;for&nbsp;Sustainable&nbsp;Asian &nbsp;Cities &nbsp;and&nbsp;Regions\",</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: red\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"> Center&nbsp;for Sustainable&nbsp;Urban&nbsp;Regeneration&nbsp;(cSUR),The&nbsp;University&nbsp;of&nbsp;Tokyo,</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;page-break-after: avoid;margin: 2px 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">荣誉和获奖</span></span></p><p style=\";line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">1.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">南京市河西北部地区控制性详细设计 &nbsp;江苏省优秀工程设计三等奖<span>&nbsp;2007</span>年</span></span></p><p style=\";line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">菏泽市古城及周边地区控制性城市设计 &nbsp;山东省优秀规划设计一等奖<span>&nbsp;2005</span>年</span></span></p><p style=\";line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">3.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">甘肃省武威市凉州区 &nbsp;新农村建设规划设计、北京市优秀工程 规划勘察设计三等奖<span>2012</span>年</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;page-break-after: avoid;margin: 2px 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">专业组织及活动</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;page-break-after: avoid;margin-left: 28px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">会议</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2009</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">年<span>3</span>月<span>24-27</span>日于清华大学组织召开住房的可支付性与市场稳定性国际研讨会</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: red\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2009</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: red\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">年<span>12</span>月<span>19</span>—<span>20</span>日于清华大学组织召开“三下乡－新农村建设高峰论坛”</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: red\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"> 2011</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: red\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">年<span>6</span>月<span>8</span>日—<span>6</span>月<span>10</span>日与清华大学组织召开第二届“社会住房和可支付性住房国际研讨会”暨中国保障性住房高峰论坛</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;page-break-after: avoid;margin: 2px 0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">出版</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;page-break-after: avoid;margin-left: 28px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">期刊文章</span></span></strong></p><p style=\";line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">1.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">邵磊，王韬，“‘房’和‘产’——有关居住的中国梦”，<span>Domus</span>中文国际版（<span>2008</span>年威尼斯国际建筑双年展中国馆特刊），<span>2008</span>年<span>9</span>月，<span>26-31</span>页</span></span></p><p style=\";line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">邵磊，王韬，“历史文化村镇中的基础设施和公共服务设施问题——河北省蔚县上苏村调研”，住区，<span>2008</span>年第<span>6</span>期</span></span></p><p style=\";line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">3.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">邵磊，“救灾要急，重建要缓——从汶川县城的争论谈起”，住区，<span>2008</span>年第<span>4</span>期</span></span></p><p style=\";line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">4.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">张杰，禤文皓，邵磊，“现代西方城市居住标准研究”，世界建筑，<span>2008</span>年第<span>2</span>期，<span>16-20</span>页</span></span></p><p style=\";line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">5.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">张杰，邵磊，中国式居住的织补策略，《时代建筑》，<span>2006</span>年第<span>3</span>期，<span>64</span>－<span>66</span>页</span></span></p><p style=\";line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">6.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">邵磊，北京旧城传统街区居民分化状况与保护更新政策思考——以什刹海烟袋斜街地区保护更新政策研究为例，《北京规划建设》，<span>2005</span>年第<span>4</span>期，<span>57</span>－<span>62</span>页</span></span></p><p style=\";line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">7.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">邵磊，社会转型与中国居住形态的变迁，《时代建筑》，<span>2004</span>年第<span>5</span>期，<span>19-23</span>页</span></span></p><p style=\";line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">8.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">邵磊，住房政策改革与居住标准的变迁，《城市开发》，<span>2003</span>第<span>9</span>期，<span>46</span>－<span>48</span>页</span></span></p><p style=\";line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">9.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">吕俊华，邵磊，<span>1978-2000</span>年城市住宅的政策与规划设计思潮，《建筑学报》，<span>2003</span>年第<span>9</span>期，<span>7</span>－<span>10</span>页</span></span></p><p style=\";line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">10.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">邵磊，北京旧城拆迁补偿政策的变迁，《城市开发》，<span>2003</span>第<span>5</span>期，<span>42</span>－<span>44</span>页</span></span></p><p style=\";line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">11.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">邵磊，</span><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">Policy &nbsp;Study on the Conservation Issues of Beijing Old City and the Historical &nbsp;Areas, Proceedings of International Workshop on Asian Approach toward &nbsp;Sustainable Urban Regeneration, September 4-7,2004, The University of &nbsp;Tokyo, Japan</span></span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;page-break-after: avoid;margin-left: 28px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">会议报告</span></span></strong></p><p style=\";line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">1.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">王亚平，邵磊，程建华，<span>Housing &nbsp;Reform in China: Managing Affordability and Market Stability</span>，住房的可支付性与市场稳定性国际研讨会，<span>2009</span>年<span>3</span>月，北京清华大学</span></span></p><p style=\";line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">邵磊，<span>The &nbsp;Problems and Trends in Historical City Conservation</span>——<span>A &nbsp;Beijing Case Study,&nbsp;</span>第二届中亚历史城市规划与保护学术会议论文集，<span>2005</span>年<span>3</span>月，</span><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">Samarkand</span></span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;page-break-after: avoid;margin-left: 28px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">著作</span></span></strong></p><p style=\";line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">1.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">吕俊华、<span>Peter &nbsp;Rowe</span>、张杰主编，《中国现代城市住宅（<span>1840</span>－<span>2000</span>）》，清华大学出版社，<span>2003</span>年出版；本人承担第三部分“改革开放<span>22</span>年以来的住宅发展”，全书第<span>189</span>－<span>276</span>页。</span></span></p><p style=\";line-height: 24px;margin-left: 73px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">吕俊华、邵磊主编，《保护城市历史风貌的探索性方案——南池子危旧房改造规划》，清华大学出版社，<span>2003</span>年</span></span></p><p style=\";line-height: 24px;margin-left: 74px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">3.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">边兰春等主编，《万科的主张（<span>1988</span>－<span>2004</span>）》，东南大学出版社，<span>2004</span>年出版。本人承担万科成长历程与社区居民调查的设计与统计分析工作。</span></span></p><p><br></p> </div>\n</div>\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"footFollow\">\n    <div class=\"title\">——<em>关注我们</em>——</div>\n    <ul>\n        <li><a href=\"javascript:;\"><img src=\"/sites/image/nimg42_1.png\" alt=\"\"></a>\n            <div class=\"layer\"><img src=\"/sites/image/img198.png\" alt=\